Benefits of This POM Structure


Separation of Concerns: UI interactions and test logic are separate.
Scalability: Adding new fields/tests requires minimal changes.
Readability & Maintainability: Easy to understand and update.
Reusability: RegistrationPage can be reused for multiple tests.



Key Improvements:

Page Objects: Created a separate RegistrationPage class for UI interactions.
Test Class: Moved test logic into a TestRegistration class.
Data Handling: Parameterized test with CSV data.
Assertions: Kept validation methods clean.


project/
│── pages/
│   ├── registration_page.py
│── tests/
│   ├── test_registration.py
│── data/
│   ├── test_pom_data.csv
│── conftest.py
│── requirements.txt



